Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.81,0:00:18.80,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.55,0:00:24.51,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,a thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.25,0:00:30.21,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.99,0:00:36.93,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,the Light struck
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:42.03,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:48.64,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:52.81,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,and fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:57.98,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\Nas the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:01:01.15,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:06.49,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:12.70,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,That blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.70,0:01:17.50,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:24.04,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:38.86,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,The Macross has been practically\Nbanished from Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.86,0:01:43.23,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the morale of the civilians\Nonboard was high enough
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.23,0:01:48.69,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,to permit the completion\Nof the kung-fu movie, {\i0}Shao Pai Long.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:55.97,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, a party is being held on\Nthe eve of the film's premiere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:55.78,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,141)}MICRO COSMOS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:01.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hikaru, what are you doing these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:03.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't seen you for ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:08.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And what is the star of tonight's\Nparty doing out here all alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.31,0:02:10.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And what is my manager doing\Ndrinking too much vodka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.89,0:02:13.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't call this "too much."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.37,0:02:16.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Too much is when I see two of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.54,0:02:18.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,which would make me extremely,\Noutrageously happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:20.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'd be twice as pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:21.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:24.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I could schedule you\Nfor twice as much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.61,0:02:27.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm joking, I'm joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.01,0:02:30.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now come inside before you catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:32.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:35.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tired? Well, no more getting sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:37.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That last time was bad enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:39.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I meant tired of all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:42.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Aah, you're just feeling blue\Nbecause the movie's done
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:44.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and your schedule's wound down a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.09,0:02:46.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not quite it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:50.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Can I get a seat reserved\Nfor the premiere?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.18,0:02:53.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's tomorrow!\NAnd it's already so late...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:54.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You really can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:02:59.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll figure something out.\NJust wait, I'll get you that seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:00.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:05.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A seat reserved for the premiere.\NA great idea if I say so myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:07.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Miss Minmay, our big star.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:10.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It is I, Jamis the villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:17.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so {\i1}sorry!{\i0} I almost ruined your\Nlovely dress, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:18.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:21.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was quite expensive, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:23.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not as expensive as mine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.63,0:03:25.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Jamis, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:28.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Jamis! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:32.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm coming, Mr. Company President!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:34.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that Minmay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:36.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, let's leave the child alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:40.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Adults should keep the company of adults, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:43.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's another thing that's making me tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:47.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay! I got a message from your manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:49.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He got you a VIP seat, A-5.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:52.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's great! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:55.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank your manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:57.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we have to make an early day\Nof it tomorrow. Time for bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:03:58.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:00.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll walk you to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:14.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. Military barracks, men's residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:18.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, is 1st Lt. Ichijo there, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:21.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Ichijo? One moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:24.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the Lieutenant is flying escort\Nfor a recon plane right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:27.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When will he be back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.13,0:04:28.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't tell you that, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:36.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. Could you please tell him he has seat A-5 waiting for him at the premiere of {\i1}Shao Pai Long{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:39.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Seat A-5. And your name, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:41.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell him it was "Nyan-Nyan."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:43.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll understand if I tell him that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:45.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Well, thanks for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,0:04:47.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, my pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.42,0:04:52.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could he have gone to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:55.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And after I got him a reserved seat too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:01.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:04.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:06.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Lieutenant! Lieutenant Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.27,0:05:07.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:10.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a phone call a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:11.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,From who?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:14.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A young lady. Said you'd know who\Nif I said "Nyan-Nyan."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:17.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really?! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:18.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Ah! And she said that seat A-5 was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:20.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}He's gone. Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:26.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Is Miss Minmay there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:28.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:32.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, can you connect me with\Nthe hotel switchboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:39.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, pick up the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:52.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if it was "just for fun," you can't go\Nwandering around dressed like that, can you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:54.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go to bed. Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:57.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:01.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was that phone call about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:03.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Minmay never calls me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:08.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh wait. {\i0}Shao Pai Long{\i1}\Npremieres tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:18.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:21.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who shot me down\Ncould be among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:31.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:34.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this crowd here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:44.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop pushing! Move back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:46.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:07:00.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Minmay sure is popular, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:03.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, good thing we got in line\Nfirst thing this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:18.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so grateful to all of you for\Nshowing up so early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:24.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the full cooperation of the\Nmilitary, {\i1}Shao Pai Long{\i0} has finally been completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:27.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, let me present the film's stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:32.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pleased to introduce Lynn Kaifun\Nand Lynn Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:47.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Minmay, how was your\Nfirst starring role?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:51.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really hard. You scolded me\Nevery day, Mr. Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:54.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! Was I really that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:58.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.\NYou were actually very kind to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:02.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, I was\Na bother to the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:06.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But I really worked on this\Nas hard as I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:08.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you all enjoy the film.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:15.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Minmay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:17.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little longer and then you\Ncan rest up backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:21.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And Kaifun, do you have anything\Nyou'd like to add?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:25.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do. It was an honor for a novice like me\Nto have been involved in such a big production.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:29.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Y'know, I heard that Minmay and Kaifun are going out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.59,0:08:30.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your warm support is what made this possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:30.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}No way! Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:31.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:34.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie! You've got a lot of nerve saying\Nthat in front of the Minmay Fan Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:37.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you guys! I can't hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.48,0:08:41.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, enough opening remarks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:43.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay, would you be so kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:44.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:51.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you like this. It's the theme\Nsong to {\i1}Shao Pai Long{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:08:59.93,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:04.71,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dancing in the sky, the silver wings
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:07.17,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shao Pai Long!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:10.41,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shao Pai Long!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:13.21,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:17.75,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The eyes of fire splitting the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:20.19,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shao Pai Long!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.78,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shao Pai Long!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:30.79,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To save a diseased city, he has returned
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:39.67,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Evil's slayer! Slayer! Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:39.97,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shao...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:47.04,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Image enhancement is complete, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:49.18,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good. Onscreen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:51.85,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...splitting the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.80,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shao Pai Long!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:58.00,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shao Pai Long!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:57.45,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to be a visual combat record.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:59.23,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a primitive combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:03.88,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would they be so eager to view\Na combat record like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:06.19,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To save a diseased city, he has returned
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.09,0:10:06.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have no idea, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:14.76,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Evil's slayer! Slayer! Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:11.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That unique fighting style...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.49,0:10:14.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could he be the one who defeated me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:17.18,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shao Pai Long!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:20.74,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is a very messiah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:28.13,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The light of hope, a messiah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:24.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:26.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Moving! Speaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:30.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, Minmay's a lot cuter in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:30.92,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shao Pai Long!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:33.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We got to see the real Minmay, in the flesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:36.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're Minmay's friends, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:40.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:48.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:51.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?! Is it the legendary power?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:56.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? They have abilities like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:11:00.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It would explain that energy barrier\Nwe encountered previously!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.81,0:11:04.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose we should inform\NLord Bodolzaa of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:19.99,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:20.98,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:22.50,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're blockin' my view!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:29.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is... this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.61,0:11:31.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart's gotten all warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:35.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This "culture" stuff gives you feelings\Nlike that all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:37.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is "culture" really that incredible?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:39.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:44.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you... Did you all do stuff\Nlike this with Minmay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:45.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:46.73,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:49.03,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And not just once or twice either!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:04.91,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Gah! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:07.73,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,1st Lt. Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:11.45,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hayase! I'm sorry.\NI sort of tripped, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:15.46,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And I just happened to be there, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:16.67,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:19.17,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd touch your butt\Nunless it was by accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:20.37,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg your pardon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:21.75,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You tell him, sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.02,0:12:23.43,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Call the cops on that pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:29.58,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me! No one respects\Nthe military anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:36.76,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:39.09,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing there, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:41.11,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I just went to see the movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.39,0:12:44.08,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And you had to leave in the middle, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:47.05,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:49.47,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Transformation initiated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:52.15,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,All civilians, please get to your shelters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:12:55.55,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They're transforming already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:58.03,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, do you know where the\Nshelter for this area is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:02.49,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to be attacked!\NWe'll have to run back to the base!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:10.52,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! The shelter's this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:14.84,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:18.50,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Minmay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:33.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay? You're not hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:37.62,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have been scared. You're safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:41.71,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't the military even give us\Nenough time to evacuate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:48.18,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a safe location. Please remain calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:51.07,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, and it was almost over, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:55.20,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to find that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:04.63,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we'll be all right if we go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:17.50,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You just had to take us around that corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:19.46,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What else could we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.70,0:14:22.56,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If a path takes a turn, you turn with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:24.89,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if we hadn't, we would\Nhave been crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:27.58,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What we should have done is\Nhead to a shelter...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:30.27,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Is that any way to talk to\Na superior officer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:34.14,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you not pull rank at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:44.72,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the attack has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:49.54,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Shammy's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:53.23,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! Phalanx Pearl Battery goes to, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:56.92,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,C-4 block, not B block!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:58.48,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please make your orders clearer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.56,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:03.88,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Captain Hayase, come back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:07.80,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, stop pouting and say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:12.16,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Ichijo, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:16.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:18.43,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's just to badmouth me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:21.55,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I get lonely when people don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:26.63,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd hear\Nyou admit that YOU get lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:28.01,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:30.65,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go. That's the Captain I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.87,0:15:34.12,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So was the one you just heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:37.74,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I was getting\Na little lonely too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:41.08,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering...\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Hey, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:42.60,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:47.34,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was wondering why they\Ntransformed so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:51.35,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm not around, 2nd Lt. Shammy is the\None who gives tactical orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:53.96,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that explains it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.24,0:15:57.00,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been specially trained\Nfor it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:01.09,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, I wonder if Max is doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:04.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, he's a genius, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:06.76,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's a better pilot than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:11.74,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a genius. His combat awareness\Nand piloting skills are top notch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:14.97,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just please don't say that in front of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:16.04,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:23.19,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Not that I think he's the type, but the thing\Nto be most afraid of when going into battle is overconfidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:26.76,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually sound like a real commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:27.73,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:31.76,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody must be talking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:39.68,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Being like this reminds me of\Nwhen we were captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:42.21,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that time was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:48.41,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It was rather difficult, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:51.70,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But things aren't nearly as desperate\Nnow as they were then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.79,0:16:54.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we're still on board the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:58.26,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We're not on some enemy ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:02.20,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, we're cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:06.24,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be out soon, as soon as\Nthe enemy attack lets up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:09.44,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But after this one ends,\Nthere will be another.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:11.90,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They just don't give up, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:15.60,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But why do you think they\Nkeep letting us live?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:18.10,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They have all that power, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:19.52,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:25.57,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You may have already heard this, but the enemy\Nseems to have split into two factions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:28.44,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,One faction thinks that we're "Protoculture,"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:32.24,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,which they fear so much they want\Nto prevent any contact with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:34.93,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there are the guys\Nwho want us dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:38.91,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. As a result, their chain\Nof command is in chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.98,0:17:42.05,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,which could be why we only\Nget these sporadic attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:45.14,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But how long can this situation last?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:49.24,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And if they get things under control,\Nwhat happens to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.50,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we get to live?\NOr will they kill us all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.66,0:17:55.75,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Purple Battery, the main enemy force\Nhas shifted toward you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:59.80,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Phalanx Ruby Battery, please provide\Nsupport for Purple Battery.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:02.32,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's gotten the hang\Nof giving orders, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:04.97,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she's still got\Na lot to learn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:07.87,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! No chatter during combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:10.04,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, aye. Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:16.71,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you getting thirsty?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:19.40,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:22.95,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo, what's wrong? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:25.96,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cola! Cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:28.91,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:31.79,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:36.77,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:39.71,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it, Ichijo. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.86,0:18:47.82,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what were you doing at the\Nmovie theater, Captain Hayase?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:49.85,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What brought that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:52.72,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. I just thought of it\Nso I figured I'd ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:57.42,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a reason you don't\Nwant to talk about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:19:01.94,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that! I just went to see\Nthe movie, same as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:05.41,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You were watching the movie,\Nwere you? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:10.32,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I was! I even heard Kaifun\Nand Minmay's intro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.51,0:19:13.36,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I never took you for\Nthe movie-going type.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:16.23,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that?!\NI'm a normal girl too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:18.73,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Girl? Yeah, right. Old lady, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:20.17,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's uncalled for!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:23.10,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause a "girl" is more...\NWait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:26.99,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman like you wouldn't have gone\Nto see the film for Minmay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:30.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! You were there for Kaifun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:31.75,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:34.87,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right! I'm right, aren't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:37.57,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hayase, you went to see\Nthat movie for Kaifun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:42.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Miss Hayase, what is it about\NKaifun that you find attractive?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:44.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop making fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:46.88,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So things are just great between\Nyou and Minmay, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:57.20,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Minmay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:03.98,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It feels like it was ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:07.70,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on... Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:11.58,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let what I said get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.78,0:20:13.62,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take it so seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:18.09,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you walk out of that theater\Nfor the same reason I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:24.59,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But how can you like a guy\Nwho hates the military?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:30.09,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He... looks a lot like someone\NI used to care for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.88,0:20:33.93,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who died before\NI could tell him anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:44.21,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:47.67,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, seeing you act like this seems\Nalmost like a put-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:51.78,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. The memories got\Na little too strong there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:53.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.47,0:20:56.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The kind of life we're living, we all\Nneed someone to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:20:59.15,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:01.48,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is retreating.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:04.15,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:07.88,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shammy, can you hurry up and\Ntake us off of battle alert?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:11.17,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a date I'd like to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.61,0:21:13.93,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's up to the Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:20.75,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think we should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.75,0:21:25.45,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Live each day to the fullest.\NThat's all we can do, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.08,0:21:27.50,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Only that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:30.61,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Only that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:51.19,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They're switching back to normal mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.42,0:21:54.94,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I guess we've been saved, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:10.55,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Want a cola?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:16.16,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Treating a superior officer?\NMaybe in ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.16,0:22:21.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, bottoms up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.92,0:22:25.03,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.73,0:22:26.64,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.71,0:22:27.94,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:30.52,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Captain, you don't need to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:42.97,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what did we expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.36,0:22:47.35,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Kaifun is her cousin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.62,0:22:50.89,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Minmay is friendly with everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.25,0:22:53.71,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But those two look like more\Nthan just "friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.00,0:23:02.09,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm gonna check out things\Non the Prometheus, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.54,0:23:08.22,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can check the hangar later, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.29,0:23:10.68,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you stay with me a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.04,0:23:12.78,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.11,0:23:34.65,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(76,114)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.11,0:23:34.65,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(335,454)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:44.05,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Britai is used by his own superior as a decoy\Nin a final plan to drive out the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.63,0:23:49.14,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Onboard the Macross,\N Minmay's concert gets underway.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.33,0:23:53.85,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,And in a successful surprise attack,\Nenemy battle pods storm the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.75,0:23:57.97,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.61,0:24:01.47,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(77,141)}LOVE CONCERT
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.45,0:24:00.92,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"LOVE CONCERT"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.30,0:24:22.45,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't follow it anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.23,0:24:29.03,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.96,0:24:35.81,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,We all keep running until the end
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.25,0:24:43.50,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.34,0:24:49.96,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.98,0:24:56.71,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.83,0:25:04.21,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.41,0:25:15.80,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The light that shines so far away
